	(text "Calcumaker 16 display — OPTIONAL aux OLED (DNP by default). J2 receives a standard 0.91\" SSD1306 128x32 I2C module (VCC GND SCL SDA; sourced separately, hand-placed with the THT digits). Wiring: J2.1 VCC<-+3V3, J2.2 GND, J2.3 SCL, J2.4 SDA. I2C at 3V3 straight from the MCU (pull-ups on the MCU board, DNP alongside). Shows full error text / SETUP / STATUS; the 7-seg glass stays primary."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
